Class InfoWindow

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lynden.gmapsfx.javascript.JavascriptObject
      • com.lynden.gmapsfx.javascript.object.InfoWindow

  • public class InfoWindow
extends JavascriptObject
    An overlay that looks like a bubble and is often connected to a marker. This class corresponds to google.maps.InfoWindow in the Google Maps JavaScript API
    Author:
    Rob Terpilowski
